data.description: Charming craftsman super close to UCA! Walk/bike/wheel to UCA from this great home with tons of character.  The tree lined street really pops in the spring. The inviting front porch is perfect for enjoying spring and summer evenings with a drink in hand. The interior features 3 beds/2 baths with hardwood floors. Primary bedroom with ensuite bathroom. Separate dining room. Fenced in back yard. Enjoy the charm of Old Town Conway and be close to all of the games, performing arts, and lectures at UCA. Foundation work has already been done to upgrade the foundation on this beautiful home.
